The path to abandon farm. One story of this farm. It belongs to a very kind old Scottish lawyer when I was a boy. I remember at that time the kind lawyer did a lot of charity work not just for my village, he did it for a large community. I haven't been to this place about 30 years. Not so much changes but people gone. My grandma told me the kind old man past away many years ago, and his family back to Scotland. Thanks Mr Kind man and Happy New Year and best wishes to your family
